metadata.name: iron master
metadata.description:
iron master. 
Despite his advancing age, he does his job with great skill and love. Now this profession is about to run out. a profession that should be passed down from father to son, now he is old and he wants his son to continue this profession. Despite the difficult conditions, he works with love and passion.

Artist : Mine Evren Ertuğrul
Location : Beyşehir / TURKEY
Size : 5006 x 3337 dpi
Date : 31.08.2013
